{"tid":2022209,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[嗇色園可信小學]個仆街教畜咁樣對待學生，做埋校長仲得了?","createTime":"2020-05-18T07:55:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T03:59:31.000Z","uid":345052,"like":49,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"d13b8c14307c2862974af62d0527b26c99ed2241","tid":2022209,"uid":345052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T07:55:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">陳梓杲，我要俾全世界知，香港新界元朗新田惇裕小學入面，潛伏住你呢啲咁嘅垃圾人渣教畜</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n事源係睇到呢篇連登post (Source: <a href=\"https://lih.kg/rKNomV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/rKNomV</a> )<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2805CmO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2805CmO.png&h=5ae9d9d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n勾起當初俾呢條仆街教畜係課室入面侮辱嘅痛苦回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔少小學師兄弟姐妹都係課堂上俾佢侮辱過，創下童年陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢以前係嗇色園主辦可信學校教書<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TDxGVft.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTDxGVft.jpg&h=7871614e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(Source: <a href=\"http://www.hoshun.edu.hk/images/30th_magazine/pdf/HoShun1103-final%2024-33.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hoshun.edu.hk%2Fimages%2F30th_magazine%2Fpdf%2FHoShun1103-final%252024-33.pdf&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCq0GH2IkZjUVJy%2ByuJI4obM%3D&h=8a1cb8f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hoshun.edu.hk/images/30th_magazine/pdf/HoShun1103-final%2024-33.pdf</a>)<br />\n<br />\n佢就最鐘意上堂羞辱D學生，尤其係女學生。<br />\n佢會特登揾野黎辱駡一D女同學，嫌佢講野細聲都可以閙成半堂，閙到個女學生喊曬口，喊到隔離班都聽到，都照閙，不聽閙，係咁閙，鬧到直頭想出手打個女同學。<br />\n<br />\n閙完就開始發神經，亂掉學生嘅功課簿、默書簿，仲要一路閙班學生係垃圾、智障，之後要我地趴係地下汁翻佢亂掉嘅野，學生嘅文具、筆袋、功課默書簿，全部散曬係地下，個刻真係覺得佢隨意踐踏緊學生嘅心靈，呢D人渣無資格做老師，當時個課室無人夠膽出聲，有D女同學忍唔住都喊埋出黎。<br />\n<br />\n對於以前讀可信小學嘅高年級學生黎講，俾呢個仆街教書應該係一世都唔會忘記嘅野黎<br />\n<br />\n而佢宜家就係另一間小學開開心心做&quot;助理校長&quot; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 過得幾愜意啊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/At92EEi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAt92EEi.png&h=546c7327&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n (Source: <a href=\"https://lih.kg/rKNomV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/rKNomV</a> )<br />\n你地睇下佢宜家笑得幾開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qfZVfbs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqfZVfbs.png&h=3ba1051a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由得佢繼續教書禍害社會，只會令更多小朋友患上心理疾病<br />\n曾經讀過嗇色園可信小學，係課堂上俾佢羞辱過嘅學生企翻出黎，揭露翻佢以前嘅惡行，唔好俾呢條人渣繼續禍害社會!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果可以，請share比各位家長，叮囑佢地保護好自己嘅小朋友<br />\n還請各位連登手足推一推呢個post，比更多舊生(如果得嘅話)關注到<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，首要清理垃圾教畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">認住呢個人渣樣</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qfZVfbs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqfZVfbs.png&h=3ba1051a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a93KSX8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa93KSX8.png&h=e242d9ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9dZevKO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9dZevKO.png&h=430b87a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gu1gJ4O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGu1gJ4O.png&h=57170146&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(Source: <a href=\"http://www.tys.edu.hk/it-school/php/webcms/public/index.php3?refid=2061&amp;mode=published&amp;nocache1589781381&amp;lang=zh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tys.edu.hk%2Fit-school%2Fphp%2Fwebcms%2Fpublic%2Findex.php3%3Frefid%3D2061%26mode%3Dpublished%26nocache1589781381%26lang%3Dzh&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCq0GH2IkZjUVJy%2ByuJI4obM%3D&h=824362c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.tys.edu.hk/it-school/php/webcms/public/index.php3?refid=2061&amp;mode=published&amp;nocache1589781381&amp;lang=zh</a>)<br />\n(Source: <a href=\"http://www.hoshun.edu.hk/images/30th_magazine/pdf/HoShun1103-final%2024-33.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hoshun.edu.hk%2Fimages%2F30th_magazine%2Fpdf%2FHoShun1103-final%252024-33.pdf&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCq0GH2IkZjUVJy%2ByuJI4obM%3D&h=8a1cb8f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hoshun.edu.hk/images/30th_magazine/pdf/HoShun1103-final%2024-33.pdf</a>)<br />\n<br />\n最後，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我屌你老母啊垃圾教畜陳梓杲</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">陳梓杲你個女宜家俾你搞成點啊？<br />\n<br />\n你係小學教書啲態度都咁撚差，你係屋企係咪虐待埋自己啲仔女啊？你同班死黑警一撚模樣，禍害人哋啲子女，宜家就逍遙法外過得幾撚開心啊。<br />\n<br />\n扮撚曬失憶走去第二度教書，以為人哋唔識你，你就可以繼續折磨你D學生啊？<br />\n<br />\n可信小學做唔落啊？要走去惇裕小學，冇人識你嘅小學做啊？<br />\n<br />\n宜家慢慢上位，你係咪好撚享受啊？屌你老母你係人渣黎架，係班家長唔撚知你以前有幾咁惡劣啊，你仲好意思做埋家教會教師委員？知唔知有幾多學生想你死啊。<br />\n<br />\n你話你有個女wor，唔知佢俾你係屋企折磨成點呢？你夠唔夠承認你無搞佢啊？垃圾<br />\n<br />\n陳梓杲，你吔屎啦屌你老母臭閪</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n校網: <a href=\"http://www.tys.edu.hk/it-school/php/webcms/public/index.php3?refid=2087&amp;mode=published&amp;nocache1589786288&amp;lang=zh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tys.edu.hk%2Fit-school%2Fphp%2Fwebcms%2Fpublic%2Findex.php3%3Frefid%3D2087%26mode%3Dpublished%26nocache1589786288%26lang%3Dzh&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCq0GH2IkZjUVJy%2ByuJI4obM%3D&h=50e10cd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.tys.edu.hk/it-school/php/webcms/public/index.php3?refid=2087&amp;mode=published&amp;nocache1589786288&amp;lang=zh</a><br />\n地址: <a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps?ll=22.498382,114.077125&amp;z=17&amp;t=m&amp;hl=zh-TW&amp;gl=HK&amp;mapclient=embed&amp;cid=15627827765373502570\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%3Fll%3D22.498382%2C114.077125%26z%3D17%26t%3Dm%26hl%3Dzh-TW%26gl%3DHK%26mapclient%3Dembed%26cid%3D15627827765373502570&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCq0GH2IkZjUVJy%2ByuJI4obM%3D&h=bba7c52a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/maps?ll=22.498382,114.077125&amp;z=17&amp;t=m&amp;hl=zh-TW&amp;gl=HK&amp;mapclient=embed&amp;cid=15627827765373502570</a>"},{"pid":"0dd1fae3b107ff5cc4c423da1dd4c12815d6fcad","tid":2022209,"uid":65638,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T08:11:52.000Z","msg":"真定假？定私怨9 up?<br />\n如果一個教師鬧學生蠢同垃圾<br />\n佢冇資格做老師"},{"pid":"e6bd2ccd3dc4054f71c57ef56702e5dcaa01b9ed","tid":2022209,"uid":345052,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"0dd1fae3b107ff5cc4c423da1dd4c12815d6fcad","tid":2022209,"uid":65638,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T08:11:52.000Z","msg":"真定假？定私怨9 up?<br />\n如果一個教師鬧學生蠢同垃圾<br />\n佢冇資格做老師"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T08:16:12.000Z","msg":"絕對唔係私怨，讀過可信嘅學生就知<br />\n宜家一定令以前嘅學生睇翻，等佢地報更多料出黎"},{"pid":"f7242bd93f1d08b03279bf421bb56ac54606ff8f","tid":2022209,"uid":24160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T09:00:22.000Z","msg":"個名點讀"},{"pid":"780b258e1c4f3243929b5e5d61550456295b6fec","tid":2022209,"uid":113222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T14:34:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f4ee8a5bee1489e4707334544214d3a5b8fe126c","tid":2022209,"uid":93251,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T14:41:40.000Z","msg":"樓主講嘅野絕對係真！<br />\n佢暴燥嘅程度同８１３速龍有得揮<br />\n好似發咗癲咁係咁鬧，又掉嘢<br />\n當年可信會收一啲能力比較差嘅學生（算叫輕微嘅弱能人士！？）<br />\n佢會係咁笑佢地<br />\n就算平時好乖好叻嘅學生都會比佢鬧到喊<br />\n我相信可